cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.NE 

This paper is primarily focused on improving the visual quality of images generated by GANs, which is a problem in computer vision (CV). Therefore, cs.CV is the most likely sub-category. The paper also proposes novel regularizers for GAN objective functions, which falls under the category of machine learning (LG, AI, NE). Additionally, the paper uses image datasets (MM), further supporting the likelihood of these sub-categories.
